      },
      "date": "2016-04-13 19:30:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nassert_DIR() is run at the beginning of each test suite, but it is also run during each run_test(). So, for every individual test, we are checking and, possibly, converting the DIR, DIR1, etc. variables. This seems excessive. \nMaybe we do want to only run this check in check_and_setup_lustre(). How do you feel about this Andreas?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "eaa7096f43f59ab4f17dabaf78cffccd1d4d4a29",
