        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2016-04-13 19:40:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nIt surprises me a bit that $DIR is being validated for each test being run.  I agree that moving it to check_and_setup_lustre() would be a good central location to validate this.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
